OL,7,FA #1.7 billion Executive-led programme
OL,8,Fis needed to tackle spiralling demand
OL,9,Ffor special education, Stormont
OL,10,FEducation Minister Paul Givan has said.
OL,12,FThe recent start of the latest school
OL,13,Fyear has seen another struggle to
OL,14,Faccommodate all those with special
OL,15,Feducational need (SEN).
OL,17,FSpeaking in the Assembly on Tuesday,
OL,18,FMr Givan urged MLAs to back his
OL,19,Fproposal for a #1.7 billion Executive-
OL,20,Fled SEN Capital Investment Programme.
