OL,4,Cpound investment is not made into
OL,5,Ceducation
OL,7,FIt is set to include new builds and
OL,8,Fcampuses for special schools as well
OL,9,Fas expansion of specialist provision
OL,10,Fin mainstream schools creating more
OL,11,Fthan 6,000 additional special school
OL,12,Fplaces and 5,000 specialist class
OL,13,Fplaces.
OL,15,FDuring the debate which followed, Mr
OL,16,FGivan clashed with the leader of the
OL,17,Fofficial Opposition, Matthew O'Toole,
