OL,5,Ceducation
OL,7,Fafter the SDLP representative claimed
OL,8,Fthat large parts of his speech had
OL,9,Fbeen written by artificial
OL,10,Fintelligence (AI).
OL,12,FMr Givan said 20% (70,000) of pupils
OL,13,Fin Northern Ireland are registered as
OL,14,Fhaving SEN, while the number with a
OL,15,Fstatement of SEN has risen by an
OL,16,Funprecedented 85% in 10 years to
OL,17,Falmost 30,000 pupils.
