OL,4,Cpound investment is not made into
OL,5,Ceducation
OL,7,F"In terms of specialist places the
OL,8,Fnumber of pupils attending a special
OL,9,Fschool has increased by 47% in the
OL,10,Fsame period (ten years), and the
OL,11,Fnumber of children in specialist
OL,12,Fprovision classes in our mainstream
OL,13,Fschools by no less than 169%," he told
OL,14,FMLAs.
OL,16,FHe said his department has invested
OL,17,F#110 million in the last two years to
OL,18,Fprovide 242 new specialist provision
OL,19,Fclasses, and 98 additional classrooms
OL,20,Facross the special school estate.
