OL,7,FBut he said numbers will increase
OL,8,Fstill further for the next decade,
OL,9,Fdescribing the scale of demand as
OL,10,F"staggering", with almost 6,000
OL,11,Fadditional special school places and
OL,12,Fmore than 5,000 additional specialist
OL,13,Fprovision places to be needed.
OL,15,FMr Givan described being at a "pivotal
OL,16,Fmoment" and urged all the parties
OL,17,Facross the Northern Ireland Assembly
OL,18,Fto support his bid for an Executive-
OL,19,Fled effort.
