OL,5,Ceducation
OL,7,FHe said action is needed now,
OL,8,Fdescribing a "central challenge facing
OL,9,Four education system and our society".
OL,11,F"This is not a challenge for one
OL,12,Fdepartment alone, it is a challenge
OL,13,Ffor the Executive as a whole," he said.
OL,15,F"Today I seek the Assembly's support
OL,16,Ffor an Executive-led and funded SEN
OL,17,Fcapital investment programme, one that
OL,18,Fwill revolutionise the facilities
OL,19,Favailable to our children and young
OL,20,Fpeople.
OL,26,@pD@NOUqD@eO]sD@AOUuD@^O]wD@AOU
