OL,3,CSEN children at risk if #1.7billion
OL,4,Cpound investment is not made into
OL,5,Ceducation
OL,7,F"The choice facing the Executive is
OL,8,Fstark, without decisive action across
OL,9,FGovernment, the system risks failing
OL,10,Fthe very children it is meant to
OL,11,Fprotect.
OL,13,F"Our special schools have reached
OL,14,Fcapacity, many are housed in outdated,
OL,15,Fdeteriorating buildings, spaces that
OL,16,Flack adequate therapy rooms, and fall
OL,17,Fshort of the standards required to
OL,18,Fdeliver modern holistic care.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
