OL,4,Cpound investment is not made into
OL,5,Ceducation
OL,7,F"All straightforward special school
OL,8,Fsolutions have been exhausted, the
OL,9,Fvast majority of special schools do
OL,10,Fnot have any physical internal or
OL,11,Fexternal space for further development
OL,12,Fand new special schools and dual
OL,13,Fcampus sites at existing schools are
OL,14,Ftherefore required across Northern
OL,15,FIreland."
OL,17,FHe added: "We are at a pivotal moment,
OL,18,Fa fork in the road.
