OL,3,CSEN children at risk if #1.7billion
OL,4,Cpound investment is not made into
OL,5,Ceducation
OL,7,F"Working closely with my department
OL,8,Fthe Education Authority has today
OL,9,Fpublished comprehensive plans to
OL,10,Fexpand, modernise and transform our
OL,11,Fspecial schools estate.
OL,13,F"But this vision can only be realised
OL,14,Fwith significant dedicated capital
OL,15,Finvestment.
OL,17,F"Without an Executive-funded programme
OL,18,Fwe will remain trapped in a cycle of
OL,19,Femergency planning, unable to provide
OL,20,Fthe specialist facilities that every
OL,21,Fchild deserves.
