OL,7,F"I cannot plan, build or deliver these
OL,8,Ffacilities children need without
OL,9,Fadditional annual earmarked capital
OL,10,Ffunding from the Executive."
OL,12,FResponding, Stormont Education
OL,13,FCommittee chairman Nick Mathison said
OL,14,Fhe welcomed the focus on special
OL,15,Feducation but questioned whether the
OL,16,F500 new specialist provision classes
OL,17,Fcan be delivered given challenges to
